vimdiff commands

]c :        - next difference
[c :        - previous difference
do          - diff obtain
dp          - diff put
zo          - open folded text
zc          - close folded text
:diffupdate - re-scan the files for differences

Delete all lines not containing 16082017
:v/\v16082017/d  

ctrl + r to redo, u to undo
